es on Afro-juju crooner, Sir Shina Peters, for the impact and longevity of his career which has spanned over 35 years in the music industry. May 25, 2019 In "Entertainment" Thousands of music lovers and artistes  who thronged the Eko Hotel and Suites, Lagos, for  the year's  Copyright Society of Nigeria, COSON, Song Awards which held last Sunday night would not forget the outcome of the show  in a hurry. November 11, 2017 In "Entertainment"